{
  "stem": "268.7",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- somehow, it was made up in Potsdam whenever any boundaries were drawn between Stalin, Roosevelt, Churchill, and the French President that the Elbe River is going to be demarcation line, which plays a big-- a big-- which made a big difference in my-- in my liberation because the American and English troops stopped at the Elbe River.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't cross it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They waited for the Russians to come in from the east.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they made an agreement to-- to unite in that particular village, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it's a known fact now about how it all happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I had no-- no idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I figured they-- my friends were telling me, discouraging me from-- from trying make a break because I-- I might get killed in-- at-- at the very last moment.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I had no choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was not [? really ?] an act of courage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a act of desperation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as I said, I had no more food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Water was the only sustenance I could get on the next stop.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I figured, the next village we come, I'll try to make a break for it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We came to a little village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know-- don't know the name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It-- it was too dark to read, and I wasn't even interested.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I-- I do remember talking to the guard who changed-- you know, I told-- we were all German.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I asked him, what day is today?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, well, why you-- what do you want to know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You got an appointment or some kind or something?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, he laughing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I says, no, I just want to know because my birthday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's April, isn't it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was April now in 1945, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
